			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Colony Barracks using the debugbook\r\n- Approach Krustine and the Skull Lashers - don't get too close or interrupt the blessing, but let it complete.\r\n- You can also interrupt the blessing and take your way out of it.\r\n- After this, they will move on into their behaviours - Krustine will send the Skull Lashers on their way with this AD"
				},
